‚Ä¢ Rely more on specificity than on the order of selectors
  ‚û• But, rely on order when using 3rd-party stylesheets - put your stylesheet last
‚Ä¢ pseudo-class counts as 1 class in specificity
‚Ä¢ How units are converted from relative to absolute (pixels)
  ‚û• % based calculations uses the parent`s width as the reference
  ‚û• em(lengths) uses current element`s font-size as the reference
